title: Ace Frehley, Kiss' original lead guitarist, dies
description: Ace Frehley, the longtime lead guitarist of the rock band Kiss, died Thursday after a recent fall at his home. He was 74 years old. CBS News' Vlad Duthiers looks back at his legacy.
